{"id":8207,"date":"2023-03-31T11:39:45","date_gmt":"2023-03-31T04:39:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=8207"},"modified":"2023-04-24T09:58:01","modified_gmt":"2023-04-24T02:58:01","slug":"dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-dep-tai-ha-noi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-dep-tai-ha-noi.html","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u1ecba Ch\u1ec9 B\u00e1n R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng \u0110\u1eb9p T\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ecba Ch\u1ec9 B\u00e1n R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng \u0110\u1eb9p T\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/h1>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng quan t\u00e2m v\u00ec nh\u1eefng m\u1ea7u r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y trong c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng R\u00e8m C\u1eeda hi\u1ec7n nay. R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00ean r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>1. T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 r\u00e8m g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00e8m C\u1ea7u V\u1ed3ng (R\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng, R\u00e8m Combi) l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1edfi hai l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i so le nhau t\u1ea1o \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng (l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp voan m\u1ecfng) \u0111an xen nhau. Nh\u1edd c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o \u0111an xen gi\u1eefa 2 l\u1edbp \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng theo \u00fd m\u00ecnh. L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1edbp t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p polyeste cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 90-100%, L\u1edbp l\u01b0\u1edbi (v\u1ea3i voan) v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn che ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8287\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8287\" style=\"width: 1175px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8287 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"1175\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi.jpg 1175w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-435x400.jpg 435w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-870x800.jpg 870w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-768x706.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/dia-chi-ban-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-510x469.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1175px) 100vw, 1175px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8287\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>2. Nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda kh\u00e1c. Tuy xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n sau nh\u01b0ng r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8288\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8288\" style=\"width: 1920px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8288 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1824\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-421x400.jpg 421w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-842x800.jpg 842w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-768x730.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-1536x1459.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/uu-diem-cua-rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-510x485.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8288\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #333399; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng. R\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3u r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 r\u00e8m s\u00e1o nh\u00f4m. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u \u1edf ph\u1ea7n v\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ecfng \u0111an xen nhau. Ki\u1ec3u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ea7y h\u01a1i th\u1edf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 ph\u00f3ng kho\u00e1ng<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8289\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8289\" style=\"width: 2048px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8289 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf sang tr\u1ecdng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \" width=\"2048\" height=\"1536\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-thiet-ke-hien-dai-sang-trong-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8289\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf sang tr\u1ecdng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u cao c\u1ea5p<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng v\u1ea3i polyeste cao c\u1ea5p, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, r\u00e8m c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y h\u00e8 n\u00f3ng b\u1ee9c. V\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng, c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u1ea5m \u00e1p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ea3n gi\u00f3, c\u1ea3n b\u1ee5i, gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8290\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8290\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8290 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u cao c\u1ea5p\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-chat-lieu-cao-cap-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8290\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u cao c\u1ea5p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>L\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i xen k\u1ebd v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng theo ki\u1ec3u k\u00e9o l\u00ean k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n n\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t linh ho\u1ea1t. Khi mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y s\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n k\u00e9o h\u1ebft r\u00e8m l\u00ean. C\u00f2n khi mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng th\u00ec k\u00e9o r\u00e8m xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ebfn khi k\u00edn h\u1ebft ph\u1ea7n c\u1eeda. Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p gi\u00fap r\u00e8m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t, ch\u1ed1ng n\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8291\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8291\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8291 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng linh ho\u1ea1t\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-lay-anh-sang-linh-hoat-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8291\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng linh ho\u1ea1t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>\u0110a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0u s\u1eafc kh\u00e1c. Trong \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1c gam m\u00e0u nh\u00e3 nh\u1eb7n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u gam m\u00e0u n\u00f3ng ho\u1eb7c l\u1ea1nh, r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 n\u00e2u, x\u00e1m, ghi, kem, xanh, tr\u1eafng,&#8230; Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8292\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8292\" style=\"width: 1535px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8292 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng phong ph\u00fa\" width=\"1535\" height=\"1474\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang.jpg 1535w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang-417x400.jpg 417w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang-833x800.jpg 833w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang-768x737.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-mau-sac-da-dang-510x490.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1535px) 100vw, 1535px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8292\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng phong ph\u00fa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafp r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ho\u1eb7c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u00f4ng s\u1edf. D\u00f9 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o, r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng v\u1eabn ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00eam tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8293\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8293\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8293 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-phu-hop-voi-nhieu-khong-gian-510x383.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8293\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn.\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ed3ng k\u1ec1nh m\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn. Nh\u1edd v\u00e0o \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n, d\u1ec5 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u0169ng s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y s\u1ef1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8294\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8294\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8294 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2560\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-2048x2048.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-kich-thuoc-nho-gon-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8294\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1ec7 sinh\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u Polyeste c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb5n m\u1ecbn, kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c v\u1ec7 sinh c\u0169ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc kh\u0103n v\u00e0 \u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lau ch\u00f9i khi r\u00e8m b\u1ecb d\u00ednh v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n c\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c th\u00e1o r\u00e8m ra v\u1ec7 sinh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8296\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8296\" style=\"width: 1620px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8296 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1ec7 sinh\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh.jpg 1620w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-de-dang-ve-sinh-510x340.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8296\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1ec7 sinh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 3 &#8211; 5 n\u0103m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1edd v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a s\u1ee3i polyeste cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt may hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8297\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8297\" style=\"width: 1920px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8297 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao-394x400.jpg 394w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao-788x800.jpg 788w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao-768x780.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao-1512x1536.jpg 1512w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-cau-vong-tai-ha-noi-co-tuoi-tho-cao-510x518.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8297\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>3. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd r\u00e8m c\u1eeda. Khu v\u1ef1c t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng r\u00e8m nh\u1ea5t \u1edf hai tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Khu\u1ea5t Duy Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 T\u00f4n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng. N\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Ph\u1ed1 R\u00e8m n\u01a1i quy t\u1ee5 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng r\u00e8m l\u00e2u n\u0103m, quy m\u00f4 l\u1edbn. Do \u0111\u00f3, m\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng r\u00e8m lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8301\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8301\" style=\"width: 861px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-8301 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi.jpg\" alt=\"R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i 36 T\u1ed1 H\u1eefu, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i\" width=\"861\" height=\"894\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi.jpg 861w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi-385x400.jpg 385w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi-770x800.jpg 770w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi-768x797.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/rem-phu-thanh-36-to-huu-thanh-xuan-ha-noi-510x530.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 861px) 100vw, 861px\" title=\"\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8301\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i 36 T\u1ed1 H\u1eefu, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i 36 T\u1ed1 H\u1eefu, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 n\u00fat giao gi\u1eefa L\u00ea V\u0103n L\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Khu\u1ea5t Duy Ti\u1ebfn. R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t\u00a0 trong nh\u1eefng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u00e0 b\u00e1n l\u1ebb r\u00e8m c\u1eeda l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 r<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-vai-nhat-ban\">\u00e8m v\u1ea3i cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u,<\/a> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/rem-sao-go\">r\u00e8m g\u1ed7<\/a>, <a style=\"color